    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/b9596c2e659640f9bd5ecaa8a153745d.avif?t=1754569809\" width=560 height=152 /></span><br><br>撒旦忘记带走那些该下地狱的禽兽<br>那就由我来当他们的引路人吧…<br><br>是夜，她向窗外的月亮祈祷<br><br>血洒上铺的无头男尸<br>精神错乱的灵异主播<br>餐厅地下室挂在肉钩上的恶鬼<br>还有操场边无声呐喊的雕像<br><br>这一切无不宣示着：祂来了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><br>《猫不语》是一款都市传说题材的恐怖悬疑解谜游戏，故事发生在一间废弃的试验中学，实习记者赵雪与秦鸿受命调查废弃学校失踪事件，看似只是校园霸凌引发的暴力案件，但背后的秘密远不止于此，一场惊心动魄的死亡冒险开始了……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/22447110f8da93a800f71336943a7e02.poster.avif?t=1754569809\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/22447110f8da93a800f71336943a7e02.webm?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/22447110f8da93a800f71336943a7e02.mp4?t=1754569809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精心设计的恐怖氛围<br></li><li>多支线剧情，多结局<br></li><li>内含暴力血腥内容，容易受到惊吓的玩家不宜体验<br></li><li>有猫猫！<br></li><li>强行塞入了一些我母上大人的画作</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748890/extras/39365903c2716d1a408ac45d7bed9f7c.avif?t=1754569809\" width=616 height=196 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本游戏内所有角色及实拍部分角色，均年满十八岁。本游戏内含有少量暗示伤害动物等内容，但未对任何动物造成实质性伤害。</h2>",
